{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:1",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ",
      "translation": "A challenger asked for a punishment bound to come[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1] In the Hereafter. The pagans of Makkah had challenged the Prophet (ﷺ) in ridicule by asking Allah to bring upon them His punishment. See 8:32."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:2",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ",
      "translation": "upon the disbelievers, which none can avert,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:3",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ",
      "translation": "from Allah, Lord of the pathways of ascent,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:4",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ",
      "translation": "by which the angels and the Spirit[2] will ascend to Him on a Day[3] the length of which is fifty thousand years.",
      "footnotes": "[2] i.e., the angel Gabriel.\n [3] The Day of Judgment will be an extremely long day."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:5",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا",
      "translation": "So be patient [O Prophet] with beautiful patience.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:6",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا",
      "translation": "Indeed, they see this [punishment] far off,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:7",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا",
      "translation": "but We see it to be close at hand.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:8",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ",
      "translation": "On the Day when the sky will be like molten brass[4]",
      "footnotes": "[4] Or \"murky oil.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:9",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ",
      "translation": "and the mountains will be like dyed wool[5],",
      "footnotes": "[5] While disintegrating."
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:10",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا",
      "translation": "and no close friend will ask about another,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:11",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ",
      "translation": "even though they will see one another. The wicked will wish he could ransom himself from the punishment of that Day by offering his children,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:12",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ",
      "translation": "and his wife and his brother,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:13",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ",
      "translation": "and his kindred who stood by him,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:14",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ",
      "translation": "and everyone on earth, just to save himself.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:15",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ",
      "translation": "By no means![6] It is a raging Flame,",
      "footnotes": "[6] An emphatic denial, meaning \"It will never be.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:16",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ",
      "translation": "that will strip off the scalps[7].",
      "footnotes": "[7] Referring to the skin of the head or of the body extremities, which will be burned away by severe heat and flames."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:17",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "It will call everyone who turned their backs and disobeyed,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:18",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "and amassed and hoarded wealth.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:19",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا",
      "translation": "Indeed, man was created impatient:",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:20",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا",
      "translation": "when evil befalls him, he bewails,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:21",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا",
      "translation": "but when good fortune comes his way, he becomes tight-fisted –",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:22",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ",
      "translation": "except those who pray,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:23",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ",
      "translation": "who are steadfast in their prayers;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:24",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ",
      "translation": "and who give a due share[8] of their wealth",
      "footnotes": "[8] i.e., obligatory charity; zakah."
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:25",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ",
      "translation": "to the beggar and the dispossessed;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:26",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ",
      "translation": "and who firmly believe in the Day of Judgment;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:27",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ",
      "translation": "and those who fear the punishment of their Lord –",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:28",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ",
      "translation": "for none can feel secure from their Lord’s punishment –",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:29",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ",
      "translation": "and those who guard their private parts[9],",
      "footnotes": "[9] i.e., their chastity and honor from immoralities."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:30",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ",
      "translation": "except from their wives or bondwomen[10] whom they own, for then they are not to be blamed.",
      "footnotes": "[10] i.e., female slaves or slave-girls."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:31",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ",
      "translation": "But whoever seeks beyond that, it is they who are the transgressors.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:32",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ",
      "translation": "and those who fulfill their trusts and pledges;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:33",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ",
      "translation": "and who are upright in their testimonies;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:34",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ",
      "translation": "and who take due care of their prayers;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:35",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ",
      "translation": "they will be honored in gardens[11].",
      "footnotes": "[11] Of Paradise."
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:36",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ",
      "translation": "What is the matter with the disbelievers that they are rushing towards you [O Prophet][12],",
      "footnotes": "[12] i.e., rushing to deny you."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:37",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ",
      "translation": "from the right and from the left, in crowds[13]?",
      "footnotes": "[13] Some pagans of Makkah gathered around the Prophet (ﷺ) mocking and opposing him, claiming that if there is in fact a Hereafter, they would enter Paradise before the believers."
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:38",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ",
      "translation": "Does everyone of them aspire to enter a garden of bliss?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:39",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ",
      "translation": "By no means! We have created them from what they know[14].",
      "footnotes": "[14] i.e., from a disdained fluid."
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "verse_number": 40,
      "page_number": 570,
      "verse_key": "70:40",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
